AVRDUDE-OSD
**************************

Description:
This patch applies osd progress display of avrdude programming tool. 

Example video:
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FfPgpg37Vf0

Dependencies:
Patch depends on Xosd library, therefore it's for linux only.

Installation:
Patch is tested and confirmed working against avrdude-5.11.
 1) unpack Your avrdude sources anywhere You like
 2) copy osd.patch into source directiory 
 3) apply patch by invoking "patch -p1 < osd.patch"
 4) configure sources "./configure --enable-osd" 
 5) compile & install.


